main event: A witness observed a round or elliptical object estimated to be 8-9 feet in diameter drifting to the south-west at an altitude of 1,000 feet.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 5543.3 seconds,The object was reported to be moving at an altitude of around 80,000 feet,The investigation concluded that the object was probably a balloon,The witness documented the observation as an air-visual type,The source of the report is identified as Civ.Jilian.
